    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a helpful summary of the safety side. However, some industry leaders and researchers argue that heavy regulation could actually be a net negative—either by slowing down life-saving breakthroughs or by giving a massive advantage to adversarial nations who won't follow the same rules. How would you address those concerns?",
